换了Z8，说明他是被Z8的功能吸引了。仅仅一星期后就以不习惯为由换掉，而且这么在意佳能有没有机械快门，我猜是不是听说了关于Z8没有机械快门的一些负面言论？ 所以有没有机械快门真的很重要吗？"},"attached_info":"CkAIo6Cbjoqf/fhsEAMaCTExMjUwNzEzNiDen6W7BjAAOCRAGnIKNzY1Mjc5MjYzNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1e5847f3fc64db80f83f3f2a414165c8_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1737544689.622652","card_id":"Q_10037869738","target":{"id":10037869738,"title":"从哪一刻开始，你对「出差」这件事祛魅了？在出差过程中又发生过哪些印象深刻的故事？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/10037869738","type":"question","created":1737303897,"answer_count":118,"follower_count":171,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1203,1575,3822706,3829343],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"年轻时向往过像成熟的职场人那样，在机场、高铁办公，也很向往能够出差的工作。但是真正听前辈们的意思，都是非常厌恶频繁出差的，这是为什么，又都经历了什么？ 《焕新吗？朋友》正在热播中，这是一档由知乎出品，聚焦消费决策和消费观念焕新的微综艺。 ✨有奖活动主链接：《焕新吗？朋友》火热播出中"},"attached_info":"CkIIo6Cbjoqf/fhsEAMaCTExMjk4MzY2MyDZzrS8BjAAOKsBQBtyCzEwMDM3ODY5NzM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"46 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-98338888972c4ae212dbff2e53f608f5_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1737544689.623367","card_id":"Q_9903962342","target":{"id":9903962342,"title":"为什么我引体向上能做 15 个以上，但干活抬东西却没劲呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/9903962342","type":"question","created":1737167150,"answer_count":33,"follower_count":49,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[61060],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我可以一口气做80个俯卧撑、100个深蹲、但是有几次从楼上往下抬柜子、跟本抬不"},"attached_info":"CkAIo6Cbjoqf/fhsEAMaCTExMjk1NjkzMiCuoqy8BjAAODFAHHIKO